1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,960
Partying is weakness for the soul, my friend, so I try and avoid it.

2
00:00:04,760 --> 00:00:10,300
I have given every single thing, every ounce of my life to this craft,

3
00:00:10,440 --> 00:00:12,620
to perfecting my craft, and I continue to do so.

4
00:00:13,040 --> 00:00:15,100
In the process, I have lost my mind.

5
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:21,260
To regular society, to people who wake up at 9 a.m.,

6
00:00:21,260 --> 00:00:23,900
who clock out at 5 p.m.,

7
00:00:23,900 --> 00:00:25,960
they would look at me and say, I've lost my mind.

8
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:28,620
But me, I have found it almost.

9
00:00:29,420 --> 00:00:32,500
My name is Conor McGregor. I'm a professional MMA fighter.

10
00:00:32,880 --> 00:00:35,259
My dream is to be world lightweight champion in the UFC.

11
00:00:36,719 --> 00:00:38,039
My dream is to be number one.

